# Image Upload Service


## API upload
```
[POST] /
{"data": "result_from_readAsDataURL"}
```

Example uploading an image:
```
curl http://localhost:7070 -X POST -H 'Content-Type: application/json' --data '{"data": "data:image/png;base64,"}'
```

Response:
```
{"status":"success","message":"OK","data":"91f04161cae920ee09e818a173a6ec9ce3b36cef"}
```


## Get image
Image should be get using web server static files hosting like ngnix or caddy.

Eg.,
```
http://localhost:8080/imageupload_data/91f04161cae920ee09e818a173a6ec9ce3b36cef
```
